            <div class="tab">
                <img src="images/home/paperclips.png" class="paper-clips">
                <div class="tab-content">
                    <img src="images/home/meetInstagram.png" class="meet-instagram" alt="Meet cashbery."/>
                    <p>
                        It’s a <b>fast</b>, <b>beautiful</b> and <b>fun</b> way to share your life with friends through a series of pictures.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Snap a photo with your iPhone, choose a filter to transform the look and feel, send to Facebook, Twitter or Flickr – it’s all as easy as pie. It’s photo sharing, reinvented.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Oh yeah, did we mention it’s free?
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <a href="http://itunes.com/apps/cashbery/"><img src="images/home/appStoreBadge.png" alt="Available on the App Store"/></a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    
